00:49:02,681 --> 00:49:03,681
1944 On 29th April, Nancy arrived in occupied
France and worked with the French Resistance.

673
00:49:03,681 --> 00:49:04,681
On 11th September, she was sent to Paris to
help the British and French armies.

674
00:49:04,681 --> 00:49:05,681
1945 The Second World War ended.

675
00:49:05,681 --> 00:49:06,681
Nancy received many honours after the war,
such as the George Medal from the UK.

676
00:49:06,681 --> 00:49:07,681
1949 Nancy returned to Australia.

677
00:49:07,681 --> 00:49:08,681
She tried to become a politician in Sydney,
but wasn't successful.

678
00:49:08,681 --> 00:49:09,681
1951 - 1958 She moved back to England and
got an office job with the British secret

