00:49:09,681 --> 00:49:10,681
service.

680
00:49:10,681 --> 00:49:11,681
In 1957, she married a British army pilot,
John Forward.

681
00:49:11,681 --> 00:49:12,681
1960 She returned to Australia with her husband.

